Name: hgversion
Version: 0.1.8
Summary: automatic version generator from a mercurial repository
Home-page: http://limedav.com/hg/hgversion/
Author: Tim Olsen
Author-email: tolsen@limespot.com
License: Apache 2.0
Description: hg_version
        ==========
        
        hg_version dynamically determines the version of your project by
        examining your project's mercurial repository.
        
        To use, just copy hgvers.py into your project.  Your projects version
        is then available from hgvers.version after importing hgvers
Keywords: mercurial hg version
